# Optional. The pipeline works WITHOUT this — it falls back to the local `claude`
# CLI (headless, uses your Claude Code login). Setting a key makes each
# per-document model call go through the Anthropic API instead: ~10x faster and
# fully deterministic, which speeds up the verify→retry loop.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and paste your key. `.env` is gitignored.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional overrides:
# INDEXER_MODEL=claude-opus-4-8
